Welcome to the OLCAtool-support wiki!

Here you can find documentation on how to use the online OLCA tool and just enough information on the [[OLCA]] (Outcome Likelihoods Causal Analysis) approach that OLCAtool supports.

OLCAtool and this documentation (plus the [[network examples]] and associated software, such as the [[OLCA file translation tool]] of OLCA file format to others for import export to alternative software) are all in beta, so you will always be able to help by contributing comments, corrections and suggestions for improvement.

